\subsection{Sync vs Async}{

The \code{async} parameter controls execution mode for all API methods:
\itemize{
\item \code{async = FALSE} (default): methods return results directly.
\item \code{async = TRUE}: methods return \link[promises:promise]{promises::promise} objects that resolve to
the same types.
}

The \code{promises} package must be installed for async mode (a \code{Suggests}
dependency).
